ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of Ukraine Concerning Youth Mobility
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF UKRAINE CONCERNING YOUTH MOBILITY; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
